article_title: Despite hundreds of supporters at Capitol, Insure Tennessee dies again

article_metadata.description: NASHVILLE -- Republican Gov. Bill Haslam's proposed Insure Tennessee plan flopped for a second time Tuesday in a Senate committee and that's thrown the House effort into confusion with two top supporters disagreeing over whether to try to move it today in a subcommittee there.
